{"lemma":"ثُلَّةٍ","slug":"ثُلَّةٍ","root":"ث.ل.ل","root_slug":"ث-ل-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/ث-ل-ل","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"ثُلَّة","root":"ثلل","pos":"N","occurrence_count":3},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n4598","n4599","n4600"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AB%D9%8F%D9%84%D9%8E%D9%91%D8%A9%D9%8D"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"bunch of people, crew, caboodle"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/θul.la/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n4598","headword_ar":"ثَلَّةٌ","root":"vl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"earth that is taken forth from a well:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S, M, K:) and the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mud that is taken forth from the bottom of a well:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M:) and the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"space upon which is cast the earth taken forth from a well, around its mouth;"},{"kind":"text","text":"which space, when the well has been dug in a place that is not the property of any one, belongs exclusively to the owner of the well: (A 'Obeyd, T:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vulalN","text_ar":"ثُلَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) ―         -b2-  ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"val~apN mavoluwlapN","text_ar":"ثَلَّةٌ مَثْلُولَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A grave"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"turobapN","text_ar":"تُرْبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"filled up with earth, after it has been dug."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A thing that is made of clay,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mud,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"like a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"manaArap","text_ar":"مَنَارَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.], (K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the desert, for the sake of its shade."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K. [Erroneously written by Golius and Freytag"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maval~apN","text_ar":"مَثَلَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and compared to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maZal~apN","text_ar":"مَظَلَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".])       -A3-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Wool,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S, M, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"alone:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a portion of wool collected together:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Er-Rághib, TA:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wool and goats' hair"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aEar","text_ar":"شَعَر"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and camels' hair"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wabar","text_ar":"وَبَر"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"together;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Aboo-Yoosuf, T, S, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"but not the second of these alone, nor the third alone:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Aboo-Yoosuf, T, S:) or it signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"camels' hair"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wbr","text_ar":"وبر"},{"kind":"text","text":") also: (T:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wool and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$Er","text_ar":"شعر"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wbr","text_ar":"وبر"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"together;"},{"kind":"text","text":"but none of these alone. (M.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kisaA='N jiy~idu Alv~al~api","text_ar":"كِسَا=ءٌ جِيِّدُ الثَّلَّةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is said to mean"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ksA'","text_ar":"كساء"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of good wool:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Habolu val~apK","text_ar":"حَبْلُ ثَلَّةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a rope of wool."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) It is said in a prov.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA taEodamu SanaAEN val~apF","text_ar":"لَا تَعْدَمُ صَنَاعٌ ثَلَّةً"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A clever woman is not without wool"},{"kind":"text","text":"to spin or weave when she has nothing else to do]: applied to a skilful man. (TA.) And you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Einoda fulaAnK val~apN kaviyrapN","text_ar":"عِنْدَ فُلَانٍ ثَلَّةٌ كَثِيرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one has much wool and goats' hair"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$Er","text_ar":"شعر"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and camels' hair"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wbr","text_ar":"وبر"},{"kind":"text","text":"). (Aboo-Yoosuf, S.) [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN kaviyru Alv~al~api","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ كَثِيرُ الثَّلَّةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[sometimes] means (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one has much hair on his body."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A flock of sheep"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"goats,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, M, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"whether many or few:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"many thereof:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K:) or specially"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a flock of sheep:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sheep, absolutely:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a numerous flock of sheep:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(ISk, T, S, K:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"numerous sheep and goats together:"},{"kind":"text","text":"many goats are not thus called; but are called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HayolapN","text_ar":"حَيْلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Aboo-Yoosuf, S, M:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vilalN","text_ar":"ثِلَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, K,) which is extr., (M,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vilaAlN","text_ar":"ثِلَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (M, K.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Many pieces of money;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"much money;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vul~apN","text_ar":"ثُلَّةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Ibn-'Abbád, K.)       -A4-  In relation to the times of camels' coming to water, ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY mawaAridi AlA_ibili","text_ar":"فِى مَوَارِدِ الاـِبِلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", TA, [in the copies of the K,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fY","text_ar":"فى"},{"kind":"text","text":"is omitted, and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mawaAridu","text_ar":"مَوَارِدُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is put for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mawaAridi","text_ar":"مَوَارِدِ"},{"kind":"text","text":",]) The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"interval of two days,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"keeping from water during two days, between two drinkings."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA. [The word to which this signification is assigned is erroneously written by Golius and Freytag"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maval~apN","text_ar":"مَثَلَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and explained as meaning “Locus ubi aquantur cameli postquam per biduum non biberint.”])"}],"source_refs":["T","S","M","K","ISk"]},{"entry_id":"n4599","headword_ar":"ثُلَّةٌ","root":"vl","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A party of men;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a company of men:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a numerous company."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Bd in lvii. 13.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN laA yaforuqu bayona Alv~al~api waAlv~ul~api","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ لَا يَفْرُقُ بَيْنَ الثَّلَّةِ وَالثُّلَّةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one will not distinguish"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"between a flock of sheep or goats and a company of men."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Z, TA.) ―         -b2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"val~apN","text_ar":"ثَلَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["S","M","K"]},{"entry_id":"n4600","headword_ar":"ثِلَّةٌ","root":"vl","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Death;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a state of perdition"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"destruction;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K;) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"valalN","text_ar":"ثَلَلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, M, K;) which latter is also an inf. n. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"val~a","text_ar":"ثَلَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifying “ he killed, ” or “ destroyed: ” (As, S, K:) pl. of the former"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vilalN","text_ar":"ثِلَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.)"}],"source_refs":["As","S","K"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}